data.description: **SELLER TO PROVIDE PERCENTAGE OF BUYERS LOAN AMOUNT FOR INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN!** This Stunning updated beauty with new, gorgeous facelift inside & out sits perfectly on tranquil golf course. Large estate size lot with fabulous pool & incredible views. Both formals plus office, game room, loft & walk-in attic. Welcome entry & incredible great room with built-ins open to sparkling kitchen. Massive bedrooms & wonderful closets. Primary Suite is complete with sitting area, fireplace & door leading to the backyard oasis. Enjoy patio, pergola, balcony, & picturesque views year-round. Soft designer colors & Exquisite floor plan includes 4 full baths. This Showstopper could easily be converted to 4 or 5 bedrooms to Meet Your Needs. Spacious, Light & Bright. Better Than New & Move In Ready! Huge storage building with driveway to accommodate all your hobbies. Golfer’s Paradise & Luxurious Lifestyle You Deserve. Your Dream Home in HJISD Available Now! Roof 6/2023. Welcome to Paradise!
